Dictionary Translator (English to German)

Description

This Python program allows users to input an English word and get its German translation using a predefined dictionary. It serves as a simple translation tool for quick word lookups.

Features

Accepts an English word as input.

Searches for its German translation in a dictionary.

Displays relevant translated words.

Ensures proper input validation.

Files

german_dictionary.py (Main script)

How to Run

Prerequisites

Ensure you have Python installed on your system.

Execution

Run the following command in the terminal:

python german_dictionary.py

Example Input & Output

Input: hello
Output: Translations of 'hello': German: hallo

Future Enhancements

Expand the dictionary to include more words.

Support additional languages.

Add an API integration for real-time translations.

Implement a GUI for better user experience.

